<section class="section section--alt who-i-work-with">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-layout">
      <div class="content-side">
        <h2 class="section-title">For Owners Who Want Assets, Not Just Code</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          I don't work with everyone. I work best with business owners who have traction but are stuck in the "Founder's Trap."
        </p>
        
        <ul class="qualifier-list">
            <li class="qualifier-item">
                <div class="check-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <strong>Revenue: $500k – $5M</strong>
                    <p>You have a proven business model, not just an idea. You have cash flow to invest in efficiency.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="qualifier-item">
                <div class="check-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <strong>Problem: "I'm the bottleneck"</strong>
                    <p>You are the only one who knows how the "secret sauce" works. If you take a vacation, the business stalls.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="qualifier-item">
                <div class="check-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <strong>Goal: A system that runs without you</strong>
                    <p>You want to move from "Operator" to "Owner." You need software assets that execute your process automatically.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="visual-side">
        <div class="quote-card">
            <blockquote>
                "Projects typically run $15k – $150k. If we're not a good fit, I'll tell you upfront. No sales pitch, just strategy."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="author">- Gera Yeremin</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
    .who-i-work-with {
        background-color: var(--color-surface-alt);
    }

    .split-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: var(--space-12);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .section-intro {
        font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
        max-width: 540px;
    }

    .qualifier-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .qualifier-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--space-4);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: var(--space-2);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .qualifier-item:hover {
        background-color: rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.05); /* very light accent */
    }

    .check-icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        background: var(--color-accent-light);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--color-accent);
        margin-top: 2px;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .qualifier-item:hover .check-icon {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .check-icon .icon {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
    }

    .text strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    }

    .text p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .quote-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: var(--space-8);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-md);
        position: relative;
    }
    
    .quote-card blockquote {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-style: italic;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .quote-card .author {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .split-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-8);
        }
        
        .section-intro {
            margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        }
    }
</style>
